@startuml
title State - AI Review Summary Cache Lifecycle

[*] --> Missing
Missing --> Generating : Request summary
Generating --> Cached : Generate success
Generating --> Failed : Generate error
Failed --> Generating : Retry/refresh
Cached --> Stale : Data changed or TTL exceeded
Stale --> Generating : Refresh
Cached --> Cached : Read cache hit
Cached --> [*]
@enduml
